scene.message:
A cold wind blows in{nl}
from beyond the door.{waitkey}{clearbox}The door is frozen solid{nl}
and won't budge.{waitkey}{ret}

Jack Frost: Hee-ho!{nl}
We transferred here from the{nl}
Demon Mountain past the door!{waitkey}{clearbox}Jackie: Hee-ho!{nl}
It's cooler over here,{nl}
nicer to live in.{waitkey}{clearbox}Jack Frost: School's fun,{nl}
huh, Jackie!{waitkey}{clearbox}Jackie: Eh, it's so-so.{waitkey}{clearbox}Jack Frost: I wonder if I can{nl}
make a hundred friends?{waitkey}{clearbox}Jackie: I doubt it.{waitkey}{clearbox}Jack Frost: ......Hee-ho?{waitkey}Human girls don't talk{nl}
so coldly, y'know.{waitkey}{clearbox}Jackie: Hee-hooo??{nl}
Humans are so difficult.{nl}
It's tiring.{waitkey}{ret}

Jack Frost: Hee-ho!{waitkey}{clearbox}Clear one tower, and one{nl}
door to the Demon Mountain{nl}
opens. Why's that?{waitkey}{clearbox}Jackie: Hee-ho!{nl}
It's just that age, y'know.{nl}
The mountain has its{nl}
reasons.{waitkey}{clearbox}Jack Frost: Hee-ho?{waitkey}Anyway, the door{nl}
opens!{waitkey}{ret}

Jackie: Hee-hooo... Nothing{nl}
fun's happened lately, hee-ho.{waitkey}{clearbox}Jack Frost: Hee-ho!{nl}
Shall I set the school{nl}
on fire?! Fwooosh!{waitkey}{clearbox}Jackie: Don't. Mistakes of{nl}
youth and all that.{waitkey}Besides, it's hot.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Who's the one who{nl}
casually built a{nl}
snowman?!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: My toes are going{nl}
numb.{waitkey}{clearbox}Honestly, the drama club!{nl}
Why pick "The Snow Queen"?{nl}
No "Queen of Eternal Summer"?{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm no good with the cold.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Kyaa~~♥{nl}
Look, look, those plushies~♥{nl}
So pretty~~♥♥{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hey, check it out!{nl}
There's a weird creature!!{nl}
Going "hee-ho, hee-ho."{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Talk to 'em and{nl}
turns out they've had it{nl}
rough, those two.{waitkey}{clearbox}And so young, too.{waitkey}Kuhh~~! It's enough to{nl}
make me cry.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Oh! It's a Jack Frost!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Be careful!! Its cute{nl}
appearance is a disguise{nl}
to lure people in.{waitkey}{clearbox}They say anyone who{nl}
approaches unguarded is{nl}
frozen by its blizzard{nl}
breath!!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Innocence and cruelty{nl}
are two sides of one coin.{nl}
Be careful!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: How many "Mirror{nl}
Shards" have we got now?{nl}
Show me the "Mirror Frame."{waitkey}{ret}
